制造；照相机及器材销售；贸易经纪；国内贸易代理；货物进出口；电池制造；电池销售；电池零配件生产；电池零配件销售；电子专用设备制造；电子元器件与机电组件设备销售；电子元器件与机电组件设备制造；电力电子元器件销售。（除依法须经批准的项目外，凭营业执照依法自主开展经营活动）。\n            - table [ref=e328]:\n              - rowgroup [ref=e329]:\n                - row \"工商信息 企业店铺 认领企业 企业风险 企业年报\" [ref=e330]:\n                  - cell \"工商信息\" [ref=e331]:\n                    - link \"工商信息\" [ref=e332] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://aiqicha.baidu.com/detail/compinfo?pid=xlTM-TogKuTw4yAPs1ZyDOKHlY7PqRxyiwmd&fr=ald_zl_jbxx&&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技&tab=basic&subtab=business\n                  - cell \"企业店铺\" [ref=e333]:\n                    - link \"企业店铺\" [ref=e334] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://aiqicha.baidu.com/detail/compinfo?pid=xlTM-TogKuTw4yAPs1ZyDOKHlY7PqRxyiwmd&fr=ald_qy_zl_shop&&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技&tab=basic&subtab=sale\n                  - cell \"认领企业\" [ref=e335]:\n                    - link \"认领企业\" [ref=e336] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: http://aiqicha.baidu.com/claiminterest/index?fr=ald_rlqy&&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技\n                  - cell \"企业风险\" [ref=e337]:\n                    - link \"企业风险\" [ref=e338] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://aiqicha.baidu.com/detail/compinfo?pid=xlTM-TogKuTw4yAPs1ZyDOKHlY7PqRxyiwmd&fr=ald_zl_qyfx&&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技&anchor=risk\n                  - cell \"企业年报\" [ref=e339]:\n                    - link \"企业年报\" [ref=e340] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - /url: https://aiqicha.baidu.com/detail/compinfo?pid=xlTM-TogKuTw4yAPs1ZyDOKHlY7PqRxyiwmd&fr=ald_zl_nb&&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技&tab=basic&subtab=annual\n            - generic [ref=e341]:\n              - link \"8位相关人员\" [ref=e342] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: https://aiqicha.baidu.com/detail/compinfo?pid=xlTM-TogKuTw4yAPs1ZyDOKHlY7PqRxyiwmd&fr=personlist_alad&pd=aen&from=ps&query=厦门鹿匠科技&subtab=directors\n                - generic [ref=e343]: 8位相关人员\n              